data.description: PRiCE IMPROVED!  BEAUTIFUL 3BR/2BA SPLIT BEDROOM RANCH ON A .89 ACRE LOT.  Includes spacious living room with a cathedral ceiling and corner gaslog fireplace; formal dining room, kitchen with custom cabinets and corner pantry; sunny breakfast area; large owner’s bedroom with tray ceiling and walk-in closet; owner’s bath with garden tub, double vanity, and separate shower; hardwood floors; tile floors in the bathrooms and laundry room, 2-car finished garage,  rocking chair front porch, rear deck; detached storage shed and metal carport.  Must see!
